Targeting these two criteria, Huang et al. [14] proposed a “ranking, filtering, and selection” (RFS) algorithm to down-select regimens. In RFS, all regimens are first ranked according to a univariate summary score across individual endpoints (such as the weighted mean \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
